function updatePairs(uint256[] _pairIndices, tuple(string from, string to, tuple(address feed1, address feed2, uint8 feedCalculation, uint256 maxDeviationP) feed, uint256 spreadP, uint256 groupIndex, uint256 feeIndex, uint256 pairId)[] _pairs)
